<ENAMEX TYPE="OKAY">The 2000 National Trade Estimate Report on Foreign Trade Barriers , released by the Office of the U.S. Trade Representative , singled out Canada for restricting trade in agricultural products , EU members for subsidizing the Airbus consortium and Japan for refusing to open its telecommunications sector .
